courses.learning_outcomes:
* Understand range of career possibilities;
* Demonstrate insight into character traits, personal passions, strengths and areas of growth;
* Exhibit confidence and poise during job interviews; and
* Produce effective CVs and online profiles.

* Demonstrate strong leadership skills;
* Resolve interpersonal tensions while fuelling change;
* Recognize and embrace diversity and inclusion;
* Enhance team productivity through skilful communication;
* Develop fundamental awareness of information security best practices in the workplace; and
